snippet.textDisplay: Commenting here after ending most beautiful relationship of my life. 4 years of absolute bliss and her silly talks. This song has always been so special to us. It was cold midnight, she was laying in my arms, then this beautiful song played. we both cried like kids knowing that every word of this song is something what we want to tell each other. When we listened to this song for the first time, I told her that we are not going to listen to this song anymore. Because I am going to ask you to marry me while playing this song in the background. Till then don't listen to it, so it can remain special to us. It describes the life we both have imagined. But this could not happened, caste came between us. My family is getting me engaged next month. I am broken from inside, looking at my future which is going to be without her. Because I know i wont be able love anyone after her. I am losing a part of my soul, and it hurts a lot. Today I am listening to this song for the last time, as a coward who could not fulfill his promise. Would never listen to again in my whole life. This song haunts me now. If she looks at this comment in future she would know that it is me, her lover, her silly Pillu, who has seen nothing but love in her eyes. My username will tell her that it is me, her fellow bird, who is now going away from her, I am not alive anymore. I can feel my soul leaving my body in the form of tears. Oh god, why it is so hard. I hope she finds the love she deserves, Love you to the moon and back my Motu. But  please always keep a part of me in your heart, don't think about me, don't talk about me to anyone, don't mention my name to anyone, just whenever you are feeling that you are not loved remember that there is this guy who has nothing but your memories. Love you my love, always yours :)
